### 🆕 MODULE F — Expense Report for Purchased Items
**Inspired by:** Notebook Page 2, Item #1

**Purpose:** Structured monthly expense reporting system with mandatory manager and admin verification.

**Business Rules (from notebook):**
- 🔴 **Manager**: Must write the name of the person who actually handles the money
- 🔴 **Submit**: Submit ONCE A MONTH — on the 30th (last day of each month) to Super Admin
- 🔴 **Uses**: Must clearly specify the purpose of the money used
- 🔴 **General Affairs**: All employees must receive approval from the administrative officer

**Features:**
- ✅ Date, Details, Specification
- ✅ Income Amount, Expense Amount, Remaining Amount
- ✅ Fund User (who physically handled the money)
- ✅ Status: Draft → Submitted → Approved/Rejected
- ✅ Monthly submission lock (submit once, on the 30th)
- ✅ Super Admin approval workflow
- ✅ PDF export of monthly expense report

**Database Table:**
```sql
CREATE TABLE expense_reports (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  office_id UUID REFERENCES offices(id),
  report_month DATE NOT NULL, -- first day of that month
  status TEXT DEFAULT 'draft' CHECK (status IN ('draft','submitted','approved','rejected')),
  submitted_at TIMESTAMPTZ,
  submitted_by UUID REFERENCES users(id),
  approved_by UUID REFERENCES users(id),
  approved_at TIMESTAMPTZ,
  rejection_reason TEXT,
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
);

CREATE TABLE expense_items (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  report_id UUID REFERENCES expense_reports(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  item_date DATE NOT NULL,
  details TEXT NOT NULL,
  specification TEXT,
  income_amount NUMERIC DEFAULT 0,
  expense_amount NUMERIC DEFAULT 0,
  remaining_amount NUMERIC GENERATED ALWAYS AS (income_amount - expense_amount) STORED,
  fund_user UUID REFERENCES users(id),
  purpose TEXT NOT NULL,
  currency TEXT DEFAULT 'USD',
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
);
```

**Page Route:** `/expenses`  
**Access:** Staff (own office, draft & submit); Super Admin (review & approve all)

